Help for NETSPLIT:

NETSPLIT allows you to monitor server splits.

構文: NETSPLIT LIST

Lists all servers currently split from the network
and how long they have been disconnected.

構文: NETSPLIT REMOVE <server>

Removes a given server from the netsplit list.

コマンド例:
   /msg &nick& NETSPLIT REMOVE moocow.int

